New Features and Important Changes in ctools 00-05-02

Author(s) : Juergen Knoedlseder

October 11th, 2012


1. Introduction
---------------
This document briefly summarizes executable by executable the most
important changes made since the last release of ctools.


2. Configuration
-----------------
The dlopen() check on Linux systems has been corrected as it failed
always due to a problem when loading the shared libgamma.so.1
library. I'm now sure why this happened. Anyhow, the libgamma.so.1
library is no longer required for the test, and now the dlopen()
capability is correctly tested.


